OL,3,CSNP urge Reeves not to cut Isa tax-
OL,4,Cfree allowance
OL,6,FThe SNP has urged the Chancellor not
OL,7,Fto cut the tax free allowance on cash
OL,8,Fsavings accounts.
OL,10,FReports have suggested Rachel Reeves
OL,11,Fcould announce the measure next week,
OL,12,Fdropping the threshold from #20,000
OL,13,Ffor cash individual savings accounts
OL,14,F(Isas).
