OL,3,CSNP urge Reeves not to cut Isa tax-
OL,4,Cfree allowance
OL,6,FSuggestions of the shift have raised
OL,7,Fconcerns among banks, while consumer
OL,8,Ffinance expert Martin Lewis claimed it
OL,9,Fcould match up to other unpopular
OL,10,Fdecisions taken by the Labour
OL,11,Fadministration in the past year,
OL,12,Fincluding the cut to personal
OL,13,Findependence payments (Pip) and the
OL,14,Fwinter fuel payment.
OL,16,FSNP economy spokesman, Dave Doogan,
OL,17,Fsaid the move could "clobber" 1.3
OL,18,Fmillion people in Scotland who have
OL,19,Fcash Isas.
