OL,3,CSNP urge Reeves not to cut Isa tax-
OL,4,Cfree allowance
OL,6,F"Rachel Reeves seems determined to
OL,7,Fmake this Labour Government one of the
OL,8,Fleast popular in history with its
OL,9,Fausterity cuts and tax hikes hitting
OL,10,Fevery part of society and leaving
OL,11,Ffamilies worse off," he said.
OL,13,F"First, the Labour Party went after
OL,14,Fpensioners and disabled people with
OL,15,Ftheir winter fuel and disability cuts,
OL,16,Fthen they went after farmers and small
OL,17,Fbusinesses with their tax hikes, and
OL,18,Fnow they are coming after millions of
OL,19,Fhard-pressed families who are simply
OL,20,Fdoing their best to save for their
OL,21,Ffutures. They are totally out of touch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]uD@AOU
