OL,3,CSNP urge Reeves not to cut Isa tax-
OL,4,Cfree allowance
OL,6,F"People are sick to the back teeth of
OL,7,Fthis Labour government making it
OL,8,Fharder for people to get by.
OL,10,F"Under Keir Starmer, Brexit Britain is
OL,11,Falready suffering from soaring living
OL,12,Fcosts, poor wages and a personal
OL,13,Fsavings crisis.
OL,15,F"The UK Government should be helping
OL,16,Fpeople not launching another Labour
OL,17,FParty tax grab ` and dipping their
OL,18,Ffingers into people's life savings.
