OL,3,CSNP urge Reeves not to cut Isa tax-
OL,4,Cfree allowance
OL,6,F"This blow to savers is already
OL,7,Fproving to be deeply unpopular with
OL,8,Fvoters and, as consumer champions like
OL,9,FMartin Lewis have warned, it could be
OL,10,Fanother winter fuel and Pip level
OL,11,Fcontroversy for millions of families
OL,12,Fwho are angry with this out-of-touch
OL,13,FLabour Government."
OL,15,FResearch commissioned by the SNP by
OL,16,Fthe House of Commons Library on the
OL,17,Fissue found 30% of Scottish adults
OL,18,Freported having a cash Isa.
